So for [Nova](/blog/introducing-nova/), my goal from the start has been to make customization as easy as possible. In fact, not only can you extend Nova's default `Posts` and `Comments` collections, but you can actually easily create your own!

In this video, I'll show you how create a new `Movies` collection, then build a paginated list to display it, as well as forms for inserting and editing documents. And all of that with almost no back-end code!

